<HEADLINE>
<P>
COUP ATTEMPT AGAINST GEN. NORIEGA 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The coup attempt certainly had the clear signature of the CIA -- total failure. 
</P>
<P>
MARK NICHOLS 
</P>
<P>
Beverly Hills 
</P>
