<P>
SOUTH AFRICAN SPORTS BAN IS FAR FROM BEING EQUAL 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Can someone explain why civilization would be threatened if South African track 
and field athletes, rugby or soccer teams were allowed to compete outside their 
own country? 
</P>
<P>
If they are being ostracized for their government's policies, how come South 
African tennis players, golfers and prizefighters compete everywhere without 
detectable ill effects? 
</P>
<P>
