intercepted Craig Woodall's pass in the fourth quarter. In the final minutes 
Schearon Stewart blocked a punt out of the end zone for Mission Bay. Stewart 
rushed 16 times for 75 yards. Pat Betancourt rushed 12 times for 62 yards and 
had one touchdown and a field goal for Mission Bay (5-1, 1-0). La Jolla is 
2-3-1 and 0-1. Mission Bay's county-leading defense has allowed only 21 points 
this season. 
