Grossmont 2-A League 
</P>
<P>
Grossmont 34, Valhalla 2 -- Valhalla took a 2-0 lead when Grossmont snapped the 
ball through the end zone, but No. 10 Grossmont (5-0-1, 1-0) then rolled at 
home. Eric Harter scored on a one-yard run and a 70-yard punt return, and Keith 
Price scored on a 69-yard pass and a one-yard run. Valhalla is 2-3-1 and 0-1. 
</P>
<P>
Metro Conference 
</P>
<P>
Hilltop 15, Castle Park 13 -- Chris Costello kicked a 22-yard field goal after 
