<P>
Palomar League 
</P>
<P>
Rancho Buena Vista 42, San Dieguito 23 -- Markeith Ross scored four touchdowns 
for top-ranked RBV (3-3, 3-0). O.J. Hall scored two touchdowns with runs of 53 
and three yards for RBV. No. 9 San Dieguito is 4-2 and 1-2. 
</P>
<P>
Mt. Carmel 29, Poway 6 -- Jeff Scott rushed for 133 yards in 22 carries to lead 
host Mt. Carmel (4-2). Mt. Carmel's Mike Graves ran a fake punt 66 yards for a 
touchdown on fourth and 25. Poway is 3-3. 
</P>
<P>
Desert/Coastal League 
</P>
<P>
Holtville 7, Marian 0 -- Victor Zaragoza scored on a 2-yard run with nine 
minutes remaining for Holtville (6-0, 1-0). Marian dropped to 0-6, 0-1. 
</P>
