<HEADLINE>
<P>
CASTING QUESTION 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Thank you for doing the worst thing a publication can do for a movie -- telling 
us the ending! 
</P>
<P>
RICHARD H. ATWOOD, Santa Monica 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
Letter to the Editor 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA101489-0047 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 120383 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
October 14, 1989, Saturday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
