<TEXT>
<P>
Authorities arrested a fourth person in the Santa Barbara County slaying of a 
Caltrans engineer who was shot to death on a secluded stretch of sand used by 
nudists at El Capitan State Beach. Sheriff's deputies and a special weapons and 
tactics team surrounded an apartment in Roseville, near Sacramento, and 
arrested Rickey Lee Rogers, 24, in the slaying Sept. 21 of Phil Bogdanoff. 
