started today in the Oakland Coliseum. ; Photo, Dennis Eckersley celebrates 
after Toronto pinch-hitter Lee Mazzilli popped up to end Game 4 of American 
League playoffs. Associated Press; Photo, Dave Stewart ; Photo, Scott Garrelts 
</P>
