Exchange on Friday in moderately active trading. Most traders appeared 
unruffled, despite the 190.58-point drop in the Dow industrial index, the 
second-largest decline on record. STEVE DYKES / Los Angeles Times; Photo, 
Nicholas F. Brady; Photo, Stephen H. Axilrod 'I don't think (the market's 
