<P>
Photo, Rancho Santiago College linebacker Fred Soares, a sophomore from Villa 
Park High, is eliciting rave reviews from Coach Dave Ogas. RICK PERRY / Los 
Angeles Times; Photo, RAISING HAVOC: Rancho Santiago linebacker Fred Soares, a 
sophomore from Villa Park, enjoys making contact with the ballcarrier. 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
